snippet.title: Neural Dominion Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
A brutal cyberpunk 4X turn-based strategy game. Take control of one of 5 gangs in Technograd — a dark, crime ridden city where getting to the top is the only thing that matters. Formerly titled Ataxia. 

Wishlist on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2493210/Neural_Dominion/

Music by Waveshaper
https://linktr.ee/waveshaper
